{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "索菲 第2话 魔力、世界、人类",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110024_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "索菲",
            "context": "这、这与魔力紊乱\\n有联系呢……　",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110024_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "索菲",
            "context": "是一大发现……\\n要、要快点报告给大家！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110024_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "索菲",
            "context": "那、那个……唔……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110024_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "索菲",
            "context": "魔力紊乱的原因……\\n我或许……已经知道了……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "真的吗！？\\n请务必告诉我！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110024_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "索菲",
            "context": "唔、那个……\\n你冷静下来听我说哦。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110024_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "索菲",
            "context": "那个……\\n果、果然……没什……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "不行不行！什么没什么！　\\n快告诉我！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110024_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "索菲",
            "context": "知、知道了……那个……\\n其实这座城的魔力循环非常活跃……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110024_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "索菲",
            "context": "对……这里的循环比我此前\\n观测过的任何地方都要剧烈。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110024_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "索菲",
            "context": "或许，这就是魔力紊乱的原因呢！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "原、原来如此……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110024_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "索菲",
            "context": "虽然循环的原因我还在调查……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110024_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "索菲",
            "context": "但说不定，和这座城堡中的龙\\n有点关系……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "是、是吗……\\n兰扎卜，你懂了吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "不，完全不懂。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "唔……索菲。\\n然后呢，能消除魔力的紊乱吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110024_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "索菲",
            "context": "这、这个……\\n需要继续调查才知道……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110024_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "索菲",
            "context": "呃……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110024_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "索菲",
            "context": "这可是一大发现呢……\\n你们不吃惊吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "是吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110024_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "索菲",
            "context": "难道你不知道\\n魔力对世界的影响\\n有多大吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110024_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "索菲",
            "context": "我来稍微说明一下……\\n两位都知道魔法吧？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "嗯。这点还是知道的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "这座城里也有能使用魔法的人。\\n在战斗中非常可靠。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110024_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "索菲",
            "context": "尤蒂尔\\n你刚才所说的魔法，\\n如果没有魔力就不能发动……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110024_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "索菲",
            "context": "因为魔法是将大气中飘散的魔力\\n收集起来，转换成物理现象的招数……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "咦？啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "我想起来了！\\n好像以前学到过。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "也就是说，其实我们在不知不觉间\\n一直受到魔力的帮助。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110024_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "索菲",
            "context": "就是这么回事！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110024_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "索菲",
            "context": "魔法和魔力，以及人类之间\\n有着非常密切的关系。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110024_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "索菲",
            "context": "教会的教义里也有对吧？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110024_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "索菲",
            "context": "“人类依靠魔力带来的魔法之力，\\n不断开拓着大地”这句话。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110024_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "索菲",
            "context": "如果没有魔力，\\n说不定我们现在还用石器刀刃狩猎，\\n居住在洞穴里呢。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "原来如此……这样一想，\\n似乎就明白魔力究竟有多重要了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110024_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "索菲",
            "context": "真的吗？太好了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110024_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "索菲",
            "context": "两位对魔力\\n产生兴趣了吗！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "嗯。现在我想了解更多\\n与魔力有关的事情。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "我也是。真是不可思议，\\n你的说明能让人听得兴致勃勃呢。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110024_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "索菲",
            "context": "啊，我不太擅长\\n教人呢……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110024_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "索菲",
            "context": "魔力其实比我说的有趣多了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110024_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "索菲",
            "context": "谢谢你们对魔力萌生兴趣。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110024_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "索菲",
            "context": "首先不要忘记\\n感谢魔力哦！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "嗯！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "当然啦！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}